To view ascii-art, you are advised to install the monafonts package,
located in pkgsrc/fonts/monafonts.  Then you can make use of it by adding

	(setq navi2ch-mona-enable t)

in $HOME/.navi2ch/init.el.
You need GNU Emacs 21 or newer or XEmacs to use monafonts.
===========================================================================
